1. *Škola* je mesto gde se stiču znanja. (School is a place where knowledge is acquired.) 
2. Moja sestra je pohađala *školu* u Nemačkoj. (My sister attended school in Germany.) 
3. Deca često idu u *školu* sa velikim entuzijazmom. (Children often go to school with great enthusiasm.)
4. Ova *škola* se nalazi u centru grada. (This school is located in the city center.) 
5. U *školi* postoji veliki izbor različitih predmeta. (At school there is a wide variety of different subjects.) 
6. Učenici često ne vole da idu u *školu*. (Students often don't like to go to school.) 
7. Ona se vratila kući sa *škole*. (She came home from school.) 
8. Oni su se sastali na *školi*. (They met at school.)